Sentencas: La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3 (LSCF)-Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 (GDC) composite is one of the most promising cathode materials for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFC).
Titulo: LSCF-GDC composite particles for solid oxide fuel cells cathodes prepared by facile mechanical method

Sentencas: However, currently most commonly used synthesis techniques for preparation of LSCF-GDC composite powders are very complicated and energy-consuming.
Titulo: LSCF-GDC composite particles for solid oxide fuel cells cathodes prepared by facile mechanical method

Sentencas: In this study, a facile mechanical method to synthesize La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3 (LSCF)-Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 (GDC) composite powder was proposed.
Titulo: LSCF-GDC composite particles for solid oxide fuel cells cathodes prepared by facile mechanical method

Sentencas: Such composite powder was formed by mechanical treatment of La2O3, Sr(OH)(2), Co3O4, Fe2O3, and GDC powders using a high-speed attrition-type mill.
Titulo: LSCF-GDC composite particles for solid oxide fuel cells cathodes prepared by facile mechanical method

Sentencas: The results revealed that the LSCF-GDC composite powder was successfully synthesized through a short-duration (20 min) mechanical treatment, and the synthesized powder formed composite particles consisting of nano-sized particles.
Titulo: LSCF-GDC composite particles for solid oxide fuel cells cathodes prepared by facile mechanical method

Sentencas: Furthermore, the resultant cathode after sintering at 900 degrees C exhibited very low polarization resistances of 0.08, 0.17, 0.38, and 0.69 Omega cm(2) at temperatures of 800, 750, 700, and 650 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: LSCF-GDC composite particles for solid oxide fuel cells cathodes prepared by facile mechanical method
